      <title>舒尔茨称已准备好讨论德国提前大选的时间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/scholz-says-ready-to-discuss-timing-of-germany-s-snap-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨表示，只要反对派议员支持他在任期结束前通过的立法，他愿意讨论提前选举的时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/scholz-says-ready-to-discuss-timing-of-germany-s-snap-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 14:54:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
